ng ST, Kowey PR "Bioavailability of Amiodarone tablets administered with and without food in healthy subjects." Am J Cardiol 87 (2001): 432-5[5] "Product Information. Cordarone (amiodarone)." Wyeth-Ayerst Laboratories, Philadelphia, PA.', 1767363020);
